OL,3,CCost of household waste collection in
OL,4,CGuernsey increases for 2026
OL,6,FThe cost of throwing away household
OL,7,Fwaste in Guernsey has gone up once
OL,8,Fagain, after hikes to bin sticker
OL,9,Fprices.
OL,11,FGuernsey's bin sticker policy is a
OL,12,F"Pay As You Throw" system for general
OL,13,Frubbish, requiring a paid sticker on
OL,14,Feach black bag for collection, with
OL,15,Ftwo sticker types (orange for 50L,
OL,16,Fgreen for 90L) to encourage waste
OL,17,Freduction.
OL,19,FBut as of 2026, the price of stickers
OL,20,Fhas increased.
