OL,6,FA green sticker for a 90 litre black
OL,7,Fbin has increased by 29 pence from
OL,8,F#3.38 to #3.67.JAnd an orange sticker
OL,9,Ffor 50 litres is going up by 16 pence
OL,10,Ffrom #1.88 to #2.04JAn increase of
OL,11,F8.5% for both.
OL,13,FThese stickers cover general waste
OL,14,Fdisposal costs, while a separate
OL,15,Fannual bill covers fixed costs for
OL,16,Frecycling services, and stickers are
OL,17,Fbought from shops.
