OL,3,CCost of household waste collection in
OL,4,CGuernsey increases for 2026
OL,6,FThe scheme was launched by Guernsey
OL,7,FWaste to fill an operating deficit,
OL,8,Fbut the scheme raised #3 million less
OL,9,Fthan expected in the first three years.
OL,11,FThis led to annual increases of 5%
OL,12,Fplus RPI being introduced from 2022 to
OL,13,F2025.
OL,15,FBut a further amendment towards the
OL,16,Fend of last year has seen further
OL,17,Fhikes introduced to try and close the
OL,18,Fgap.
