OL,3,CCost of household waste collection in
OL,4,CGuernsey increases for 2026
OL,6,FIslander's have had a mixed reaction
OL,7,Fto the increases, with one person
OL,8,Fsaying, "I'm not surprised. Costs
OL,9,Falways go up but our wages don't"
OL,11,FWith another adding, "I think that the
OL,12,Frecycling has been so successful that
OL,13,Fwe're now being penalised for it".
OL,15,FBut one islander said they don't
OL,16,Fbegrudge the cost going up at all,
OL,17,F"you used to have to put everything in
OL,18,Fyour metal bin, but now it's so much
OL,19,Feasier to sort it."
