OL,3,CCost of household waste collection in
OL,4,CGuernsey increases for 2026
OL,6,FMajor changes to the island's approach
OL,7,Fto recycling in 2019 saw a huge drop
OL,8,Fin the amount of black bag waste the
OL,9,Fisland produces.
OL,11,FAs part of the approved 2026 budget,
OL,12,Fthe Guernsey Waste Board and States'
OL,13,FTrading Supervisory Board agreed that
OL,14,Fall Guernsey Waste gate fees and
OL,15,Fcharges (both commercial and
OL,16,Fhousehold) should be increased by RPIx
OL,17,F+ 5%.
